A warm tropical evening scene in Singapore's Marina Bay area, Studio Ghibli style animation aesthetic with soft watercolor textures and gentle lighting. Two small figures walk together along a waterfront promenade, silhouetted against the glowing city skyline with its distinctive architecture reflected in calm waters. Lush tropical plants frame the scene with oversized monstera leaves and swaying palm fronds. The sky transitions from deep orange to purple twilight, with a few early stars appearing. Warm lantern lights dot the pathway, creating a welcoming atmosphere of friendship and collaboration. The scene conveys arrival, partnership, and the magic of international connection in an exotic locale.
